descript.abstract: Outline of South Carolina based on the DLG 1:24,000 county boundary data set. Includes 3 mile limit along coast.
descript.purpose: The following data set shows the outline of South Carolina and also includes the 3 mile limit along the coast.
descript.supplinf: This data set was created by merging all of the county boundaries from the DLG 1:24,000 scale county boundary data set into one polygon.
